ng","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"resurgence","count":1},{"word":"report","count":1},{"word":"phenomena","count":1},{"word":"hall","count":1},{"word":"exit","count":1},{"word":"absorbing","count":1},{"word":"echoes","count":1},{"word":"human","count":1},{"word":"body","count":1},{"word":"entirely","count":1},{"word":"unprecedented","count":1},{"word":"jump","count":1},{"word":"conclusions","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"proper","count":1},{"word":"details","count":1},{"word":"giant","count":1},{"word":"scythe","count":1},{"word":"sound","count":1},{"word":"crownless","count":1},{"word":"higher-ranked","count":1},{"word":"enormous","count":1},{"word":"moon","count":1},{"word":"looming","count":1},{"word":"reminds","count":1},{"word":"sightings","count":1},{"word":"supposedly","count":1},{"word":"past","count":1},{"word":"war","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"put","count":1},{"word":"captures","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"specific","count":1},{"word":"bad","count":1},{"word":"built","count":1},{"word":"structure","count":1},{"word":"spheres","count":1},{"word":"goal","count":1},{"word":"extract","count":1},{"word":"pure","count":1},{"word":"cannot","count":1},{"word":"guarantee","count":1},{"word":"eliminated","count":1},{"word":"arrival","count":1},{"word":"revived","count":1},{"word":"accidentally","count":1},{"word":"captured","count":1},{"word":"sometimes","count":1},{"word":"memory","count":1},{"word":"manifestations","count":1},{"word":"sentient","count":1},{"word":"beings","count":1},{"word":"encountered","count":1},{"word":"manifestation","count":1},{"word":"suspect","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"unconscious","count":1},{"word":"mind","count":1},{"word":"anomalies","count":1},{"word":"hiding","count":1},{"word":"simulation","count":1},{"word":"'resonated'","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"lifted","count":1},{"word":"afraid","count":1},{"word":"conclusion","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"thorough","count":1},{"word":"collected","count":1},{"word":"earth","count":1},{"word":"terms","count":1},{"word":"bodily","count":1},{"word":"functions","count":1},{"word":"seem","count":1},{"word":"perfect","count":1},{"word":"health","count":1},{"word":"fact","count":1},{"word":"quite","count":1},{"word":"feel","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"general","count":1},{"word":"retroact","count":1},{"word":"rain's","count":1},{"word":"effects","count":1},{"word":"subsiding","count":1},{"word":"observing","count":1},{"word":"sharp","count":1},{"word":"decline","count":1},{"word":"norfall","count":1},{"word":"barrens","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1},{"word":"currently","count":1},{"word":"monitoring","count":1},{"word":"attacks","count":1},{"word":"design","count":1},{"word":"safer","count":1},{"word":"route","count":1},{"word":"received","count":1},{"word":"word","count":1},{"word":"soldiers","count":1},{"word":"large","count":1},{"word":"targeting","count":1},{"word":"troops","count":1},{"word":"defend","count":1},{"word":"surrounded","count":1},{"word":"slowly","count":1},{"word":"closing","count":1},{"word":"recapture","count":1},{"word":"nearby","count":1},{"word":"recharge","count":1},{"word":"hold","count":1},{"word":"little","count":1},{"word":"longer","count":1},{"word":"send","count":1},{"word":"coordinates","count":1},{"word":"backup","count":1},{"word":"port","count":1},{"word":"wish","count":1},{"word":"luck","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"The Academy has noted a concerning rise in Tacet Field activities. Please use caution when exiting the city.","quest_name":"Rewinding Raindrops","quest_id":114000020},{"text":"Remember to check your Terminal signals, and wear the Academy's protective suit correctly...","quest_name":"Rewinding Raindrops","quest_id":114000020},{"text":"...And don't forget to stay hydrated. Now, I have experiments to run. Take care.","quest_name":"Rewinding Raindrops","quest_id":114000020},{"text":"You are alright, it seems.","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"It won't take long before the Reverberations disappear and the Etheric Sea vanishes. Once that happens, the Resonance Beacon signals will come back.","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"The Tacet Field will dissipate, biding time for its next resurgence.","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"...","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"We'll need to report the unusual phenomena here to the City Hall and the Academy.","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"Let's make our exit.","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"...","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"Absorbing Echoes with the human body is not entirely unprecedented.","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"Let's not jump to conclusions without enough data and proper analysis.","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"Rover.","quest_name":"Utterance of Marvels: I","quest_id":139000025},{"text":"Can you give us some more details?","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"A giant Tacet Discord with a scythe... It doesn't sound like the Crownless. Might be even higher-ranked.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"An enormous moon looming above you... Now, this reminds me of the unusual sightings that supposedly happened during a past war...","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"This is the first time we've run into anything like this since we put the training ground into use...","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"The Sonoro Sphere captures everything that once happened in a specific time and place, be it good or bad.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"We built this simulated training ground after the structure of Sonoro Spheres.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"Our goal was to extract pure Remnant Energy with the simulated Sonoro Sphere, but we cannot guarantee that all \"abnormal frequencies\" were eliminated.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"Your arrival may have revived the \"abnormal frequencies\" we accidentally captured.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"Remnant Energy sometimes give rise to memory manifestations of sentient beings. You may have encountered one such manifestation.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"I suspect it could have something to do with your unconscious mind.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"Such anomalies could have been hiding in the simulation, and they 'resonated' with your subconscious. Or perhaps... they were lifted from your subconscious in the first place.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"I'm afraid I can't give you a conclusion yet. Not until we've run a thorough analysis on the data collected.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"I'll also check the simulated Sonoro Sphere again to see what on earth happened to it.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"In terms of bodily functions, you seem to be in perfect health... In fact, all the data look quite good.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"But if you feel anything unusual, please come find me any time.","quest_name":"First Resonance","quest_id":139000027},{"text":"General, the Retroact Rain's effects are subsiding. We are observing a sharp decline in the number of Tacet Discords in the Norfall Barrens.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Yes.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Rover, I am currently monitoring the Tacet Discord attacks from the Academy to design a safer route for you.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"We just received word from our soldiers at the emplacement. A large number of Tacet Discords are targeting the Disruptor, and our troops are doing their best to defend it.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"The Disruptor has been surrounded by the Tacet Discords, with more of them slowly closing in.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"After we recapture the nearby emplacement, it will take some more time for the Disruptor to recharge. You may need to hold out a little longer.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"I'll send you the coordinates of the Disruptor and its backup energy port. We wish you the best of luck.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004}]}